  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nA compromised renderer is able to send an extension message to another tab.  \n  \nThe browser process (extensions::MessageService) does not check ExtensionHostMsg_OpenChannelToTab message came from an extension process or a process with access to chrome.tabs.sendMessage A"
